{
  "id": "adv_event_2306_02_05_02",
  "title": "STAGE5",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ありがとうございました！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you very much!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.845850873,
      "endTime": 3.2000004767999997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 3.4703179996
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "……はぁ～～、緊張した～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Phewww‚ that was nerve-wracking!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.4703179996,
      "endTime": 6.600476710100001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.8036513329
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "いつもとは全く違う緊張感でしたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was a completely different tension than usual‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.8036513329,
      "endTime": 10.0724721432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.2703179996
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣は楽しかったよー！\nすずにゃんは緊張してたみたいだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei had fun~!\nIt seemed like Suzunyan was nervous though",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.2703179996,
      "endTime": 15.6629030865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.8703179996
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっ！　何を言っているんですの？\nわわ、私は緊張なんてする訳にゃいですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey! What are you saying?\nI-I'm not nervous at all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.8703179996,
      "endTime": 22.8175967853,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.0036513329
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "にゃい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not at all?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.0036513329,
      "endTime": 24.165124237599997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.3703169823
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "うるさいですわ！\n緊張するのは悪いことではないのですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're annoying!\nBeing nervous isn't a bad thing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.3703169823,
      "endTime": 29.4523122788,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.636983649
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、そうだね。緊張してるのはみんな同じ、だよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ that's right. We're all nervous‚ aren't we?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.636983649,
      "endTime": 35.1865301769,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.3703169823
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "それより、{user}さんとさとみさんを\n置いてけぼりにしていますよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "More importantly‚\nyou're leaving {user}-san and Satomi-san behind!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.3703169823,
      "endTime": 39.8145344735,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.0036503156
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "わわっ、ほんとだ！\nそれじゃあ、琴乃ちゃん、どうぞ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Wow‚ you're right!\nThen‚ Kotono-chan‚ go ahead!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.0036503156,
      "endTime": 44.7141465505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.9036477725
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、渚！　急に振らないでよ！\nごほん。改めて、ご覧いただきありがとうございました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Wait‚ Nagisa! Don't just suddenly pass it over to me!\nAhem. Once again‚ thank you for watching",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.9036477725,
      "endTime": 55.0000006039,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.3666672706
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.2675938447
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "今回私達はデビュー曲である『月下儚美』を選びました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This time‚ we chose our debut song‚ \"Night-blooming Beauty\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.2675938447,
      "endTime": 60.247593673000004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.456323719
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "パフォーマンスで感謝を伝える……って\n凄く難しいねってみんなで話し合ったんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Expressing gratitude through performance…\nWe discussed it with everyone‚ and it seemed very difficult",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.456323719,
      "endTime": 67.598296547,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.7896570523
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "なんだかんだいって意見は一致しましたよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But in the end‚ we all agreed‚ didn't we?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.7896570523,
      "endTime": 70.8127183755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.0229903857
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "最初のライブからの成長を見せることが一番の感謝\nだよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Showing growth from the first live is the greatest gratitude\nRight?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.0229903857,
      "endTime": 76.9229919354,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.1229883511
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "あー！　私が言おうと思いましたのに！\nまぁでも、そういうことですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahh! I was going to say that!\nAnyway‚ that's how it is",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.1229883511,
      "endTime": 84.2601312954,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.4563216845
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "嬉しい時は{user}さんやさとみさん\nみんなで喜びを分かち合って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When we're happy‚ {user}-san‚ and Satomi-san\nWe share the joy together…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.4563216845,
      "endTime": 89.979178683,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.1896550178
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "つ、辛い時にはいつもそばにいてくれたことには\n感謝していますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A-And when it's tough‚ I'm grateful for\nalways being by our side.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.1896550178,
      "endTime": 96.6333339373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.8563257535
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "お二人がいなかったら\nクリスマスのサプライズはなかったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you two weren't here‚\nthere wouldn't have been a Christmas surprise",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.8563257535,
      "endTime": 100.9854187329,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.1896590869
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "私が莉央さんと一緒にお姉ちゃんの曲を歌うことも\nなかったと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't think I would have sung big sister's song\nwithout you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.1896590869,
      "endTime": 106.17838932679999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.3871193727
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "だから、みんなとーっても感謝してるんだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ we're really grateful to you guys!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.3871193727,
      "endTime": 110.9326523622,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.1204527061
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_05-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "いつも本当にありがとうございます\n私は……私達は今大きな壁にぶつかっていると思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you so much as always\nI… We believe we're facing a big obstacle now",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.1204527061,
      "endTime": 121.6352373283,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.8439673742
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
